00:30:47.116 --> 00:30:58.274
And there are people who have pains that are no longer there—knee pains, things that are happening.

00:30:58.275 --> 00:31:04.870
People are actually getting manifestations of things and they're telling me about it. So, I give all glory to God for that.

00:31:04.871 --> 00:31:11.772
It isn't Brandon Biggs, but I'm going to say it's exciting to see manifestations of things like that.

00:31:11.773 --> 00:31:15.665
I believe God's raising up multi-billionaires in the days ahead.

00:31:15.666 --> 00:31:22.644
You know, people are so upset about BlackRock and all this stuff I've talked about.

00:31:22.645 --> 00:31:31.273
I have already talked about what it was, but I am not a financial advisor.

00:31:31.274 --> 00:31:43.731
