02:30:49.689 --> 02:30:58.916
So, if you have that, you have the sister clipboards that will go off and just go, and they go, "The sky is falling."And that's not what I'm trying to do.

02:30:58.917 --> 02:31:04.956
I never want to bring fear because I'm bringing something from the Holy Spirit.

02:31:04.957 --> 02:31:08.505
But God is not—He doesn't want to scare you; He'll prepare you.

02:31:08.506 --> 02:31:13.918
But if you're not mature, what you're hearing can scare you.

02:31:13.919 --> 02:31:24.239
And I don't want to ever bring fear to people where they can't sleep at night and go, "Brandon, you kept me up all night long."No, I'm asking you to humble yourself and to come up higher in your prayer life with Him.

02:31:24.240 --> 02:31:29.631
And some things even Jesus couldn't deliver to the disciples because they couldn't bear it at that time.

02:31:29.632 --> 02:31:37.436
He said, "I can't even tell you this right now because you don't have ears to hear this right now."And I'm not saying I'm like Jesus.

02:31:37.437 --> 02:31:51.311
I'm trying to say when you're delivering a word, the Lord says, "Know your audience."And if I was talking to a group of my prayer family, who really pray with me, I would unleash all this.

02:31:51.312 --> 02:32:01.160
But I have a caution. Do you understand what I'm saying? I hope you do, but probably you don't. And it's not my problem if you don't, I guess.

02:32:01.161 --> 02:32:10.761
But it's like there are some very dark things I've seen tonight, and you better be listening and prayed up.

02:32:10.762 --> 02:32:19.119
Be prepared. Am I saying this to scare you? If it scares you, it scares you.

02:32:19.120 --> 02:32:54.559
I can't help that. I had to tell you some of it. That river is still so strong; I can feel it pulling me.

02:32:54.560 --> 02:33:32.318
Find it. If you need a sword, buy a sword. Did you find it? Yeah, it's fine. Okay. So, this is Jesus.

02:33:32.319 --> 02:33:40.255
And to those of you that don't think Jesus had a way of protecting Himself, Jesus said this.

02:33:40.256 --> 02:33:49.034
He said to them, "But now if you have a purse, take it and also a bag.

02:33:49.035 --> 02:34:05.039
And if you don't have a sword, sell your cloak and buy one."What do you do with a sword?

02:34:05.040 --> 02:34:12.959
A lot of y'all need to read your Bible. Do you see where He says if you need a sword, sell your cloak and go buy one?

02:34:12.960 --> 02:34:16.606
What are you going to do with it? Are you going to use it to hunt?

02:34:16.607 --> 02:34:20.329
You think they used a sling or slingshot back then for hunting?

02:34:20.330 --> 02:34:29.415
But that was for protection, right? So if you need one, go buy one. Jesus told them to.

02:34:29.416 --> 02:34:38.478
And there are things coming that you may need to have something to defend your home.

02:34:38.479 --> 02:34:55.519
I'll leave that there. It's right there in the Bible. God's the God of love, right?

02:34:55.520 --> 02:35:14.799
He loves you. Jesus loves you. But even He warned the disciples. He warned them.

02:35:14.800 --> 02:35:19.576
He said to them, "But now if you have a purse, take it and also a bag.

02:35:19.577 --> 02:35:53.279
And if you don't have a sword, sell your cloak and buy one."So, I've got to be polite.

02:35:53.280 --> 02:36:01.061
But we love y'all. God bless you. Have a wonderful Memorial Day weekend. I'll be praying.

02:36:01.062 --> 02:36:09.564
I'll see what the Lord says about Saturday and Sunday, and we'll go from there—more than likely Sunday for sure, Monday.

02:36:09.565 --> 02:36:14.964
Praying over the weekend, praying over all the things that we need to pray over. We'll continue to keep praying.

02:36:14.965 --> 02:36:21.006
Keep your eyes to the skies because Jesus Christ is coming, ladies and gentlemen, and you need to know it.

02:36:21.007 --> 02:36:28.815
Keep your eyes on Him. So, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:36:28.816 --> 02:36:37.669
Jesus loves you, and we love you. God bless you and have a wonderful night.

